creator: Hely
descriptionHtml:
Pick from various (electric) shared cars, e-bikes and cargo bikes from a Hely Hub in your neighbourhood. This way, you’re always flexible, you contribute to the environment and you save on costs.

Most important features of the Hely app:
• View which vehicles are available near you
• Always everything on hand: with the app you lock and unlock all vehicles
• Start your ride immediately or reserve in advance
• Direct contact with the Hely Service Desk through mail, chat or by calling
• Useful instruction videos and FAQ’s to help you get started
• Overview of all your rides and costs
• Invite your neighbours to both enjoy €10 discount
• Take a look in the app before you start a subscription
• Sign up even when there’s no hub open near you, so you get notified when we go live in that area.

Not convinced yet? These are the advantages of Hely:
• All in one: Rent all your shared mobility with one app, one account and one subscription. Nice and clear!
• Affordable: At Hely you ride without kilometer charge and fuel is always included. You can rent a vehicle starting at just €1,50 per hour.
• Sustainable: With shared mobility you save lots of CO2, fossil fuels and you contribute to clean, low-traffic cities.
• Flexible: Pick which vehicle is most convenient at any time. Your Hely account can be cancelled every month.

More information about Hely can be found on www.hely.com. For questions, check out www.hely.com/faq or contact support@hely.com.
